OL,11,FMPs, says households need a minimum    
OL,12,Fincome to meet the cost of living.     
OL,14,FFormer work and pensions secretary     
OL,15,FStephen Crabb said the welfare system  
OL,16,Fhas "significant gaps and weaknesses". 
